description: The only Corner 800+SF 1BR, 1.5BA w/PRIVATE BALCONY&GARAGE PARKING at EchelonSeaport, a Regent Hotel Collection offering 5 star living in the heart of Boston’s Seaport. Enjoy serene southwestern views of Waterfall Pool&European-inspired Piazza offering cascades of natural light throughout the day from floor to ceiling windows. Corner Living RM offers Private Balcony, a perfect spot to start or end the day. Chef’s Kitchen fitted w/Italian Cabinetry, Thermador Apps, Island&Pantry. King Sized Primary Suite w/ample closets, Marble Bath w/glass shower. Powder RM, HW Fls throughout, in-unit laundry&motor shades complete the home. Enjoy unrivaled 50,000SF of Jeffrey Beers designed amenities-designed to be an extension of home: 3 Pools(2 Outdoor, 1 Indoor), Spa, Fitness/Yoga/Pilates, Basketball/Pickleball Court, Golf Sim, Pet Run, Lounges, Landscaped Terraces, Decks with Grills, Co-Work Space&more. Full Service 24/7 Concierge, Porter, Doormen, Valet. Dine&Shop on-site at 125,000SF Superette.
